author: @ideagirl
text:
Thank you so much. I report all the time. Now to this new address. Just so you all know. AI is illegal. No one can use any company's Intellectual Property  such as pictures, names, voices, likenesses or  signatures. This includes Fan Fiction. You must have a legal written consent contract to use anything of BTS or Big Hit or Hybe. Always report it to YouTube too because YouTube must take it off of their site because Hybe could sue them for allowing others to post illegal content. I promise you. Every AI BTS copy, video, or channel I have reported to YouTube has been taken down. How do I know? YouTube sends me an email report or their decisions on everything I report. Off subject, but I report lots of violence, which is banned. Go to Community Guidelines to read their rules. If someone is  bullying you with words that is illegal too. Know this. Sometimes it takes awhile for the video to come down.
 And sometimes it will show back up, but under another channel name. These illegal videos are like viruses. Go do your research on this. Hybe filed a lawsuit against a YouTube person. Also, V and JK also individually filed suit against this same person. BTS members are sick of defamatory rumors and fake photoshopped pics of them. These offenders will lose their cases no matter if they have a good lawyer or not. So thank you to Jose for posting this. But YOU must do your part too. You must report these people who are breaking the law. Even though a channel person posts this notice...This Is AI. Just for entertainment purposes. It's still Against the Law!!!
